'''Bothawui Shipyards''' was a [[Starship/Legends|starship]] manufacturer.

==History==
Toward the end of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothans]] began production of the [[Bothan Assault Cruiser]]. During the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], they also made a type of [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]].

